                        <code>&lt;think&gt;&lt;observation&gt;...&lt;/observation&gt;...&lt;/think&gt;&lt;answer&gt;...&lt;/answer&gt;</code>
                      </div>
                      <p>Learning: <span set:html="\\(z_t = \\langle \\hat{s}_t, a^b_t \\rangle\\)" />, learning to approximate <span set:html="\\(\\hat{s}_t \\rightarrow s_t\\)" /></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-details" id="worldmodeling-content">
                      <p><strong>WorldModeling:</strong> Explicit future state prediction</p>
                      <div class="code-snippet">
                        <code>&lt;think&gt;...&lt;prediction&gt;...&lt;/prediction&gt;&lt;/think&gt;&lt;answer&gt;...&lt;/answer&gt;</code>
                      </div>
                      <p>Learning: <span set:html="\\(z_t = \\langle a^b_t, \\hat{s}_{t+1} \\rangle\\)" />, learning to approximate <span set:html="\\(\\hat{s}_{t+1} \\rightarrow s_{t+1}\\)" /></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="strategy-details" id="combined-content">
                      <p><strong>WorldModeling:</strong> Combined current and future state reasoning</p>
                      <div class="code-snippet">
                        <code>&lt;think&gt;&lt;observation&gt;...&lt;/observation&gt;...&lt;prediction&gt;...&lt;/prediction&gt;&lt;/think&gt;&lt;answer&gt;...&lt;/answer&gt;</code>
                      </div>
                      <p>Learning: <span set:html="\\(z_t = \\langle \\hat{s}_t, a^b_t, \\hat{s}_{t+1} \\rangle\\)" />, learning to approximate <span set:html="\\(\\hat{s}_t \\rightarrow s_t, \\hat{s}_{t+1} \\rightarrow s_{t+1}\\)" /></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
